      <title>价值 7.6 亿美元的美国-新加坡海底电缆项目获批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/us-singapore-subsea-cable-seen-worth-760-million-gets-approval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[吉宝有限公司 (Keppel Ltd.) 称，首条连接新加坡和美国西海岸的海底电缆系统已获得美国登陆许可，这将增强新加坡成为亚洲领先数字枢纽的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/us-singapore-subsea-cable-seen-worth-760-million-gets-approval</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 03:10:46 GMT</pubDate>
